OL,3,CHeart expert explains Luton Town
OL,4,Ccaptain Tom Lockyer's collapse on the
OL,5,Cpitch - and what happens next
OL,7,FLuton Town's captain became the latest
OL,8,Ffootballer to suffer a cardiac arrest
OL,9,Fon the pitch this weekend, after
OL,10,Fcollapsing during the match against
OL,11,FBournemouth on Saturday.
OL,13,FIt was the second time 29-year-old Tom
OL,14,FLockyer had collapsed during a game,
OL,15,Fand he'd previously received treatment
OL,16,Ffor another heart condition - atrial
OL,17,Fdefibrillation.
